entries.name: new(type = nil, *items)
entries.desc: Creates a new list of type with items.  Valid list types are: :BULLET, :LABEL, :LALPHA, :NOTE, :NUMBER, :UALPHA

entries.name: accept(visitor)
entries.desc: Runs this list and all its items through visitor

entries.name: last()
entries.desc: Returns the last item in the list
